{% set showHeader = showComponentTitle != false %}
<section class="disclosure-group{% if not showHeader %} disclosure-group-plain{% endif %}" aria-label="Services">

{% if showHeader %}
<details>

<summary class="disclosure-header">
MY SERVICES
</summary>
{% endif %}

<div class="content-block">

<details class="disclosure-item">
<summary>Individual Psychotherapy (NY & ME)</summary>
<div class="content-block">
<hr class="rule dotted-blue-rule">

<p>I offer talk therapy to individuals who have received a psychiatric diagnosis and are responding to a significant incident in life. My clients are often facing education disruption, high conflict divorce, legal issues, or a financial crisis that is often driven by problematic behaviors.</p>

<hr class="rule dotted-blue-rule">

<p>Want to start the conversation? I offer free consultations</p>
<a href="#contact-me" class="button" id="schedule-consultation">
  Message Me
</a>

</div>
</details>



<details class="disclosure-item">
<summary>Social Work-Informed Consulting</summary>
<hr class="rule dotted-blue-rule">
<div class="content-block">
<p>
For individuals with less psychiatrically acute problems and contexts, I offer consulting services. My clients are often students, tradesmen, servicemen, developers, and creative professionals. Many feel off-course or stalled, but remain motivated and open to focused self-development as a way forward. 

While some are looking to use thoughtful discourse to better organize their thinking and direct their efforts, others are looking to increase their accountability and eliminate undesirable behaviors.

Consulting differs from psychotherapy in a few key ways:

* They follow different ethical standards.
* Consulting is non-clinical, with simpler documentation and no insurance billing.
* The focus is on professional and interpersonal goals first; behavior change and symptom reduction are secondary.
* My consulting is subscription-based and tailored to your needs.


</p>

<hr class="rule dotted-blue-rule">

<p>Want to see if this service is right for you? Schedule a free consultation.</p>
<a href="#contact-me" class="button" id="schedule-consultation">
  Message Me
</a>

</div>



</details>
</div>

{% if showHeader %}
</details>
{% endif %}

</section>